\c 12
\s Madzimambo akakundwa naIsraeri
\p
\v 1 Zvino awa madzimambo enyika vana vaIsraeri avakarova ndokugara nhaka yenyika yavo mhiri kwaJoridhani kumabvazuva, kubva pamupata weArinoni kusvika pagomo reHerimoni, nebani rese kumabvazuva:
\v 2 Sihoni mambo weVaAmori waigara paHeshibhoni, waitonga kubva paAroeri riri pamahombekombe erwizi rweArinoni uye kubva pakati perwizi, nerupandi rweGiriyadhi kusvikawo kurwizi Jabhoki mucheto wevana vaAmoni;
\v 3 uye bani kusvika kugungwa reKineroti kumabvazuva, uye kusvika pagungwa rebani, Gungwa reMunyu kumabvazuva, nzira inoenda Bhetijeshimoti, uye kubva kuchamhembe pazasi peAshidhodhi-Pisiga;
\v 4 nemuganhu waOgi mambo weBhashani, wevakasiiwa veVaRegaimu vaigara paAshitaroti nepaEdhirei,
\v 5 wakatonga pagomo reHerimoni nepaSarika nepaBhashani rese, kusvika kumuganhu wevaGeshuri nevaMaakati, nehafu yeGiriyadhi, muganhu yaSihoni, mambo weHeshibhoni.
\v 6 Mozisi muranda waJehovha, nevana vaIsraeri vakavarova; Mozisi muranda waJehovha ndokuipa vaRubheni nevaGadhi, nehafu yerudzi rwaManase, kuti ive yavo.
\p
\v 7 Zvino awa madzimambo enyika iyo akakundwa naJoshua navana vaIsraeri mhiri kwaJoridhani kumavirazuva, kubva paBhaari-gadhi mumupata weRebhanoni, kusvikira pagomo reHaraki rinokwira richienda Seiri; Joshua akaipa marudzi aVaIsraeri sezvavakange vakamurirwa, kuti ive yavo.
\v 8 Panyika yamakomo, nomumapani, nomuArabha, napamitenusirwa, nomurenje, nechamhembe; ndiyo yaiva nyika yaVaHiti, neyaVaAmori, neyaVaKenani, neyaVaPerezi, neyaVaHivhi, neyaVaJebhusi,
\v 9 mambo weJeriko ndiye mumwe; namambo weAi, pedo neBheteri, mumwe;
\v 10 namambo weJerusarema, mumwe; namambo weHebhuroni, mumwe;
\v 11 namambo weJarimuti, mumwe; namambo weRakishi, mumwe;
\v 12 namambo weEgironi, mumwe; namambo weGezeri mumwe;
\v 13 namambo weDhebhiri, mumwe; namambo Gedheri, mumwe;
\v 14 namambo weHorima, mumwe; namambo weAradhi, mumwe;
\v 15 namambo weRibhina, mumwe, namambo weAdhuramu, mumwe;
\v 16 namambo weMakedha, mumwe; namambo weBheteri, mumwe;
\v 17 namambo weTapua, mumwe, namambo weHeferi, mumwe;
\v 18 namambo weAfeki, mumwe; namambo weRasharoni, mumwe;
\v 19 namambo weMadhoni, mumwe; namambo weHazori, mumwe;
\v 20 namambo weShimironi-meroni, umwe namambo weAkishafi, mumwe;
\v 21 namambo weTaanaki, mumwe; namambo weMegidho, mumwe;
\v 22 namambo weKedheshi, mumwe; namambo weJokineamu paKarimeri, mumwe;
\v 23 namambo weDhori panyika yamakomo yaDhori, mumwe; namambo weGoimi paGirigari, mumwe;
\v 24 namambo weTiriza, mumwe; madzimambo ese akange ana makumi matatu nomumwe.
